4 main forms of communication

  email
    audience
      usually people in your team, or in teams related to the project
    structure
      should look like a formal letter
    purpose
      main avenue of communication

  documentation
    audience
      anyone who has a copy of the code base
    structure
      language specific but normal contains short discriptions of publicly accessible methods
    purpose
      inform users how to properly use your code

  stackoverflow
    audience
      Software Developer community
    structure
      short post with snippets of code and descriptions of problems
    purpose
      find solutions to unsolved problems amoungst your coworkers

  project request
    audience
      your development team
    structure
      varies on tools used and workplace norms
    purpose
      defined requirements and specifications for new developments projects as well as changes to existing products
